==================================
GNATcoverage 1.1 NEW FEATURES LIST
==================================

Copyright (C) 2012-2013, AdaCore

This file contains a complete list of new features in version 1.1 of
GNATcoverage.

An ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD) appears in parentheses after the description line.
This date shows the implementation date of the feature. Any 1.1.0w wavefront
subsequent to this date will contain the indicated feature, as will any
release issued after this one.

NF-11-KC21-020 Project file support for determination of SCO path (2012-07-12)

  GNATcoverage is now able to leverage GNAT project file to locate Source
  Coverage Obligations and control coverage analysis options. Project files
  may now specified on the gnatcov command line using options "-P" and
  "--projects". A new package Coverage is introduced in project files, where
  units of interest can be listed, and options specified.

NF-11-L725-007 Per-instance source coverage on generics (2012-12-19)

  GNATcoverage now includes support for per-instance coverage assessment of
  source level criteria on generic units, triggered by "-S instance" on the
  "gnatcov coverage" command line. This requires compiler support available
  from GNAT Pro 7.1.
